collectible.name: The Leaves of the First Mondrian Marijuana Plant of Crypto Voxels
collectible.description: This was the first crypto marijuana plant that I, before being the Crypto Dealer, planted with my friend Germs, on his land on Crypto Voxels. When we planted that seed, a huge marijuana plant was born, which emanated infinite marijuana from itself. It has a heady aroma and its seed came from the Mondrian Bag of endless marijuana. After a terrible event, this plant died and left behind 10 unaging leaves, with the proper seeds, which Germs and I shared equally. I left for my house, already intending to sow that little plant through the metaverse; and it was this seed that led me to the path of being the Crypto Dealer.
collectible.author: 0xdb08edbcf449de2a2b27448a8040935802c621f1

collectible.description: We lost our human form, but we still have some of our feelings. We are not here to do any harm, but we crave for living experiences, and the scary experience is the best one! We feed on your fear, but we hope you keep fearing forever. <3
